      "content": "but they're aging too, and they have lives and stress of their own. i don't want to be the one thing that breaks them. sometimes i lie awake thinking that if i could just... let go quietly, it would be the last truly selfless thing i could do for them. wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if things just ended before things got even worse?",
